---
// Mission — Lethwei kinship + ancient martial arts preservation
// Editorial block, kept restrained
---

<section class="py-24 sm:py-32 relative">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span
        class="text-brand-gold text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 block"
      >
        Why We Exist
      </span>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-black uppercase tracking-tighter"
      >
        Preserving Ancient Arts. <span class="text-brand-gold">Broadcasting Them Globally.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Two-image side-by-side -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div
          class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/5 bg-cover bg-center"
          style="background-image:url('/mission/kun-khmer.jpg');"
        >
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-darker via-black to-brand-dark/60 flex items-end p-4">
            <span
              class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/80"
            >
              Kun Khmer
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/5 bg-cover bg-center mt-8"
          style="background-image:url('/mission/lethwei.jpg');"
        >
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-darker via-black to-brand-dark/60 flex items-end p-4">
            <span
              class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/80"
            >
              Lethwei
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/80 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Crush Combat exists to showcase the world's most ancient martial arts
          on the global stage through broadcasting.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Khmer Flow Arena is our vehicle for <strong class="text-white">Kun Khmer</strong>
          — the 1,000-year-old striking art carved into the walls of Angkor Wat,
          now stepping onto the world's screens.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We stand alongside <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/LethweiFightingChampionship/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="text-brand-gold hover:text-white underline decoration-brand-gold/30 underline-offset-4 transition-colors"
            ><strong>Lethwei Fighting Championship</strong></a
          >, who are doing the same for Burmese bare-knuckle — celebrating an
          ancient art in its raw form, broadcasting it to the world.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-gold"
        >
          Kindred mission. Different lineage. Same fire.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
